text: "A Woman in Love (It's Not Me)" is a 1981 song by Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers. It is the second single from their fourth studio album Hard Promises. It went to number 79 in the United States. ==References== Category:1981 songs Category:Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers songs Category:Hard rock songs
title: A Woman in Love (It's Not Me)
